\section{Authenticated SharePoint access}

We keep the HTTP logic in a dedicated session class. That class reuses the
shared authenticated browser session from [[ladok3]] and adds only the extra
KTH handlers that SharePoint needs.
<<classes>>=
class OneDriveSession:
  """Read and write SharePoint files through the shared KTH session."""

  def __init__(self,
               session=None,
               username: Optional[str] = None,
               password: Optional[str] = None):
    """Create a SharePoint-capable session."""
